The paper focuses on learning and suggesting coding conventions, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The use of statistical natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning techniques (cs.LG) to learn and suggest natural coding conventions supports these categories as well. The paper also discusses the use of tools for development and release management, which could fall under programming languages (cs.PL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories.
